      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a documented rod bearing service and a professionally reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural rigidity and mechanical longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, feeding power through the factory M-Variable differential. Every bushing, damper, and seal is in optimal condition, preserving the precision of the McPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. Finished in immaculate original paint with a pristine interior, this is a turn-key analog masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
